      <title>波兰洪水后寻求欧盟在赤字削减谈判中采取宽大措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/poland-to-seek-eu-s-leniency-in-deficit-cut-talks-after-floods</link>
